          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "If you play in North American tournaments (USA or Canada), study TWL (also called NWL or the NASPA Word List). If you play internationally or in countries like the UK, Australia, or New Zealand, study SOWPODS/CSW. For casual home games, SOWPODS gives you the most options since it includes all TWL words plus extras. Many online platforms let you choose which dictionary to use."
        }
